body_html:
You appear to be using CentOS 6. If this is not the case, let me know and I'll reopen this issue.

The operating systems supported by TensorFlow are:

  • Ubuntu Linux 14.04 LTE
  • Ubuntu Linux 16.04 LTE
  • Mac OS X El Capitan
  • CentOS 7+

For other OS, please direct the question to StackOverflow and people might be able to help there.

P.S. It might be possible for you to use our contrib make build system for CentOS 6 support.

Other issues similar to this: #4725 #2806.

You appear to be using CentOS 6. If this is not the case, let me know and I'll reopen this issue.

The operating systems supported  by TensorFlow are:
- Ubuntu Linux 14.04 LTE
- Ubuntu Linux 16.04 LTE
- Mac OS X El Capitan
- CentOS 7+

For other OS, please direct the question to [StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/tensorflow) and people might be able to help there.

P.S. It might be possible for you to use our contrib make build system for CentOS 6 support.
